QUICK UPGRADE MANUAL FOR eyeOS
------------------------------

This manual is for upgrade eyeOS v0.8.x to v0.9.0.

1) Download the latest version of eyeOS from http://www.eyeOS.org.

2) Uncompress the package to a local dir.

3) Upload and replace all directories and files except the following directories:

 etc/
 home/
 usr/

5) Give full read/write permissions to the new two directories users/ and files/.

5) Run index.php and you should see the new version number at the Login Screen.

Please, read the SECURITY MANUAL.

Enjoy eyeOS!
